            "content": "<p>Meet Boost & Bloom, your scalp's new best friend. This 15ml micro-needling hair booster serum combines the power of targeted delivery with a built-in roller-ball applicator — designed to stimulate the scalp while channelling actives deep into the hair follicle. Unlike regular serums that sit on the surface, Boost & Bloom works at the source. The stainless steel roller tip gently primes the scalp, improving absorption so every drop counts. Whether you're dealing with thinning, slow growth, or a scalp that needs waking up — this serum is built to deliver results you can actually see. Compact, travel-friendly, and clinical-grade. 15ml of concentrated care in one sleek pen.</p>"
